videos.description: WR Jared Miles takes the handoff and eludes tackles all the way to the end zone, giving the Mustangs an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: SMU strikes first on 20-yard jet sweep

videos.description: William Brown finds WR James Proche across the middle, who stays on his feet and crosses the goal line to make it 21-3 Mustangs.
videos.headline: SMU expands lead with 20-yard TD pass

videos.description: LaDarius Dickens breaks loose and goes all 95 yards to the end zone, cutting the SMU lead to 28-10.
videos.headline: Houston Baptist scores first TD on 95-yard kickoff return

videos.description: SMU holder Jamie Sackville shovels a pass to TE Ben Redding, who turns the field-goal attempt into a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mustangs execute fake FG as time expires before halftime

videos.description: RB Braeden West squeezes through a hole and finds the end zone to put SMU up 42-10.
videos.headline: Mustangs pad lead with 11-yard TD run

videos.description: Backup QB Ben Hicks fires a strike to WR Judah Bell to make it 49-17 Mustangs.
videos.headline: SMU pours it on with 9-yard TD pass
